150
00:08:35,817 --> 00:08:37,667
Okay. Don't come home too late.

151
00:08:37,667 --> 00:08:38,749
All right. Have a safe ride.

152
00:08:38,750 --> 00:08:39,791
Okay, bye bye.

153
00:08:39,792 --> 00:08:41,317
Bye.

154
00:09:20,066 --> 00:09:22,866
