155
00:09:25,775 --> 00:09:28,317
Hey! What are you doing?

156
00:09:30,500 --> 00:09:32,042
Teng Teng!

157
00:09:32,625 --> 00:09:33,958
Are you all right?

158
00:09:33,959 --> 00:09:34,874
I will take you to hospital.

159
00:09:34,875 --> 00:09:36,066
