160
00:09:36,066 --> 00:09:38,375
It just hurts a lot.

161
00:09:39,417 --> 00:09:41,033
Where is he?

162
00:09:41,575 --> 00:09:43,667
F**k! He ran away.

163
00:09:43,667 --> 00:09:47,323
If I catch him, I'll beat him so badly his own parents won't recognize him!

164
00:09:47,323 --> 00:09:49,008
