166
00:10:02,542 --> 00:10:04,042
Be careful.

167
00:10:12,417 --> 00:10:13,608
Are you feeling better?

168
00:10:13,608 --> 00:10:15,317
Does it still hurt?

169
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:18,542
It doesn't hurt anymore. I don't need this.

170
00:10:18,542 --> 00:10:20,083
No way!

171
00:10:20,083 --> 00:10:22,165
Just before, it hurt so much you couldn't even walk.

172
00:10:22,165 --> 00:10:25,666
I think you should go to a hospital.

173
00:10:25,666 --> 00:10:29,542
