174
00:10:29,542 --> 00:10:33,925
Mu Ren... Have you offended anyone recently?

175
00:10:35,834 --> 00:10:37,842
No.

176
00:10:38,709 --> 00:10:43,249
But when he got close to me, I smelled

177
00:10:43,249 --> 00:10:46,800
