178
00:10:48,100 --> 00:10:52,700
Do you mean that the person, who recently broke into our house, attacked you today?

179
00:10:54,542 --> 00:10:57,875
From now on, you can't go out alone.

180
00:10:57,875 --> 00:10:59,875
Xiao Yeh or I need to be with you.

181
00:10:59,875 --> 00:11:02,100
