203
00:12:25,090 --> 00:12:27,359
Thank you, Mommy.

204
00:12:35,700 --> 00:12:38,792
Yung Chieh, why is your face bruised?

205
00:12:38,792 --> 00:12:40,959
Did you run into something?

206
00:12:40,959 --> 00:12:42,174
