208
00:12:43,583 --> 00:12:45,500
Did you offend anyone?

209
00:12:45,500 --> 00:12:48,149
I attacked someone, thinking that he was alone,

210
00:12:48,149 --> 00:12:51,250
but his friend came along and beat me.

211
00:12:51,250 --> 00:12:53,875
Are you trying to get in the news?

212
00:12:53,875 --> 00:12:56,300
How would your dad and I face people?

213
00:12:56,300 --> 00:12:59,200
Your sunames are Yeh and Lee. Mine is Fu.

214
00:12:59,200 --> 00:13:03,200
Even if my whole name was reported, it still wouldn't affect you two.

215
00:13:03,200 --> 00:13:05,874
