216
00:13:05,874 --> 00:13:10,191
No wonder you said no when I asked if you wanted to have the same surname as Dad.

217
00:13:10,191 --> 00:13:13,125
I have other plans. That's why I didn't change it.

218
00:13:13,125 --> 00:13:15,450
What other plans do you have?

219
00:13:22,834 --> 00:13:25,209
Your dad asked you a question.

220
00:13:30,083 --> 00:13:30,999
Fu Yung Chieh!

221
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:32,500
Mommy.

222
00:13:35,208 --> 00:13:37,375
He usually answers questions.

223
00:13:37,375 --> 00:13:39,475
If he doesn't want to tell us,

224
00:13:39,475 --> 00:13:41,125
it's useless to ask.

225
00:13:41,125 --> 00:13:43,458
It's not like you don't know that.

226
00:13:43,458 --> 00:13:48,750
Daddy, I'm just afraid he will do something illegal. You heard him, too.

227
00:13:48,750 --> 00:13:52,133
He's already attacking people on the street.

228
00:13:54,800 --> 00:13:58,567
Yung Chieh... Did anyone see your face?

229
00:13:58,567 --> 00:13:59,875
I wore a mask.

230
00:13:59,875 --> 00:14:02,075
There were no security cameras nearby.

231
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:04,208
My goodness.

232
00:14:04,208 --> 00:14:05,542
Daddy, listen to this!

233
00:14:05,542 --> 00:14:08,217
This was all planned.

234
00:14:08,850 --> 00:14:11,934
This evil has to be stopped at the beginning.

235
00:14:11,934 --> 00:14:14,834
- Daddy...
- All right, all right.

236
00:14:14,834 --> 00:14:16,909
Let him eat breakfast.

237
00:14:19,542 --> 00:14:21,959
Hsing Ssu has probably come back.

238
00:14:24,400 --> 00:14:27,458
That's strange! Didn't you say you were busy? Why suddenly come home?

239
00:14:27,458 --> 00:14:29,374
I knew there would be plenty of breakfast

240
00:14:29,374 --> 00:14:30,825
so I specially came to eat.

241
00:14:30,825 --> 00:14:32,375
Smart boy. I will get a bowl.

242
00:14:32,375 --> 00:14:33,542
Okay.

243
00:14:33,542 --> 00:14:35,833
- Dad.
- Sit.

244
00:14:47,150 --> 00:14:48,860
- Here.
- Thanks, Mom.

245
00:14:48,860 --> 00:14:50,866
Eat more!

246
00:14:53,800 --> 00:14:57,125
After breakfast, I need to discuss something with you.

247
00:14:57,125 --> 00:14:58,625
All right.

248
00:15:00,001 --> 00:15:02,083
The fish tastes very good.

249
00:15:02,083 --> 00:15:03,583
Okay.

250
00:15:05,700 --> 00:15:09,000
I really didn't expect that guy to be Xiao Yeh's little brother.

251
00:15:09,000 --> 00:15:12,066
It's his stepbrother. They're not related by blood.

252
00:15:12,066 --> 00:15:14,166
It doesn't matter if he came with a stepmom,

253
00:15:14,166 --> 00:15:15,875
they're still family.

254
00:15:15,875 --> 00:15:17,333
What I really don't understand is

255
00:15:17,333 --> 00:15:19,709
why attack his brother's friend for no reason?

256
00:15:19,709 --> 00:15:22,358
Also, he attacked me and not you.

257
00:15:22,358 --> 00:15:25,450
That's because you are soft and delicate,

258
00:15:25,450 --> 00:15:27,142
unlike me.

259
00:15:28,208 --> 00:15:29,817
Do you think he has a death wish?

260
00:15:32,375 --> 00:15:36,358
I told you to eat Chocola BB Pure (supplements) regularly.

261
00:15:36,358 --> 00:15:39,208
It has Vitamin B2, which maintains energy and metabolism.

262
00:15:39,208 --> 00:15:40,791
