575
00:36:07,100 --> 00:36:09,941
He was just scared of Hsing Ssu getting angry.

576
00:36:09,941 --> 00:36:10,874
Why is that?

577
00:36:10,874 --> 00:36:12,916
He values Hsing Ssu a great deal.

578
00:36:12,916 --> 00:36:15,274
He was happy when Hsing Ssu was worried about him,

579
00:36:15,274 --> 00:36:18,200
