598
00:37:27,916 --> 00:37:30,917
I like women.

599
00:37:39,540 --> 00:37:41,700
I'm not overthinking.

600
00:37:41,700 --> 00:37:46,700
When it comes to having feelings for a guy, I'm way more experienced than you.

601
00:38:08,750 --> 00:38:10,391
Stop moving.

602
00:38:10,391 --> 00:38:13,383
You have to pretend not to feel it. Otherwise, Mei Fang will realize it's fake.

603
00:38:13,383 --> 00:38:16,207
I'm not a block of wood. How can I not feel it?

604
00:38:16,208 --> 00:38:17,874
We can't always use pictures.

605
00:38:17,875 --> 00:38:20,582
At the company, we need to interact periodically.

606
00:38:20,583 --> 00:38:23,183
Then Mei Fang will think I'm making progress with you.

607
00:38:29,300 --> 00:38:31,542
Not there! It's ticklish.

608
00:38:31,542 --> 00:38:33,175
Why is it ticklish?

609
00:38:34,333 --> 00:38:36,082
Is your neck your sensitive area?

610
00:38:36,083 --> 00:38:37,342
It's not!

611
00:38:37,342 --> 00:38:39,666
