612
00:38:39,667 --> 00:38:41,547
Okay, I will find a different spot.

613
00:38:46,917 --> 00:38:48,624
Stop dodging me.

614
00:38:48,625 --> 00:38:50,416
You have to get used to my touch.

615
00:38:50,417 --> 00:38:52,499
We are both men! How can I get used to it?

616
00:38:52,500 --> 00:38:54,900
Hsing Ssu, am I right?

617
00:38:56,159 --> 00:38:58,083
I...

618
00:38:58,083 --> 00:38:59,691
Let me try.

619
00:39:26,667 --> 00:39:28,542
Is it uncomfortable,

620
00:39:28,542 --> 00:39:30,459
or do you not like it?

621
00:39:31,750 --> 00:39:33,750
It feels fine.

622
00:39:33,750 --> 00:39:36,683
But maybe it is because we are brothers.

623
00:39:42,834 --> 00:39:45,874
Hey, Kiddo, I booked a place.

624
00:39:45,875 --> 00:39:47,065
Let's fight a round.

625
00:39:47,065 --> 00:39:48,416
Do you mean now?

626
00:39:48,417 --> 00:39:49,900
Okay.

627
00:40:04,900 --> 00:40:06,300
Why does Li Cheng have to fight?

628
00:40:06,300 --> 00:40:09,208
Yung Chieh will never beat him.

629
00:40:09,208 --> 00:40:10,433
Don't worry.

630
00:40:10,433 --> 00:40:13,100
Li Cheng will know when to stop.

631
00:40:13,100 --> 00:40:14,583
One round is three minutes long.

632
00:40:14,583 --> 00:40:16,000
Three rounds.

633
00:40:16,000 --> 00:40:17,400
Okay.

634
00:40:38,060 --> 00:40:39,600
Hey!

635
00:40:41,809 --> 00:40:43,982
Didn't you say Li Cheng would know when to stop?

636
00:40:43,982 --> 00:40:47,091
Your brother sneakily attacked Li Cheng first.

637
00:41:04,900 --> 00:41:07,600
Hsiao Li Cheng, be gentle!

638
00:41:14,917 --> 00:41:16,559
Are your legs weak?

639
00:41:38,700 --> 00:41:40,200
Yung Chieh!

640
00:41:44,017 --> 00:41:46,250
Hsiao Li Cheng, didn't I say to be gentle?

641
