653
00:42:16,667 --> 00:42:18,808
I'm very protective.

654
00:42:41,892 --> 00:42:42,917
I'm not in pain.

655
00:42:42,917 --> 00:42:44,417
It's painful! How can it not be?

656
00:42:44,417 --> 00:42:46,717
If it's not painful, why did you fall on your knees in the ring?

657
00:42:57,750 --> 00:42:59,470
Press down on this.

658
00:43:23,875 --> 00:43:25,083
